Codes and commands for Chapter 1
================================

Configuring EM Express

-- dbms_xdb_config.sethttpport procedure for non-SSL connection 

exec dbms_xdb_config.sethttpport(5500);

-- dbms_xdb_config.sethttpsport procedure for SSL connection 

exec dbms_xdb_config.sethttpsport(5500);

-- Checking the XDB port

select dbms_xdb_config.gethttpsport() from dual;

